before you, a--

00:10:02.941 --> 00:10:04.555
SAM: It's me, Vax.

00:10:04.555 --> 00:10:07.025
(laughter)

00:10:07.025 --> 00:10:14.582
SAM: Hey everybody, I can fly 200,000 feet in one
second.

