left I'll start walking up the wall. I know I

00:58:05.591 --> 00:58:06.473
won't make it.

00:58:06.473 --> 00:58:09.165
MATT: Okay, you can get to the very top if you
want to.

00:58:09.165 --> 00:58:11.570
TALIESIN: Not quite, next round I'm going to pop
up.

00:58:11.570 --> 00:58:15.188
MATT: Okay, so we'll say you're right there. But
this chest is opened, so I'll turn it to the side

00:58:15.188 --> 00:58:16.629
as a reminder.

00:58:16.629 --> 00:58:18.215
TALIESIN: Knock it prone.

00:58:18.215 --> 00:58:26.877
MATT: Basically. You knocked the chest prone.
