00:58:41.775 --> 00:58:49.082
flames inside burst out in a radius. Nobody is
quite in the radius to be affected by them. You

00:58:49.082 --> 00:58:52.861
watch as the corners of the battlefield are
suddenly engulfed in flames briefly. Then the

00:58:52.861 --> 00:58:57.953
flames retract back into just very gently burning
braziers.

00:58:57.953 --> 00:59:01.218
TALIESIN: I love it. This is like Battlebots.

00:59:01.218 --> 00:59:03.588
MATT: Vex, you're up.

00:59:03.588 --> 00:59:08.153
LAURA: Okay, Grog's coming for me.

00:59:08.153 --> 00:59:09.384
TRAVIS: No.

00:59:09.384 --> 00:59:14.369
LAURA: First of all, Trinket's going to just wade
