01:10:40.906 --> 01:10:45.034
MARISHA: Five for Vex and four for Grog.

01:10:45.034 --> 01:10:47.820
MATT: All right, so Grog, you take two points of
fire damage. Vex, you take five.

01:10:47.820 --> 01:10:51.743
TRAVIS: Can I make my retaliation strike after her
melee on me?

01:10:51.743 --> 01:10:52.872
MATT: Yes, you can.

01:10:52.872 --> 01:10:59.047
TRAVIS: Okay. Reckless! Where's the crit now?
