02:28:21.772 --> 02:28:22.832
LAURA: Okay.

02:28:22.832 --> 02:28:26.228
MATT: It's a lot to coordinate. That ends your
turn, Vex. Grog, you're up.

02:28:26.228 --> 02:28:34.431
TRAVIS: I was going to leave you alone. I was
