LAURA: Doesn't.

02:29:46.840 --> 02:29:48.481
TRAVIS: No, that's the damage.

02:29:48.481 --> 02:29:49.700
LAURA: Oh. Shit.

02:29:49.700 --> 02:29:51.581
(laughter)

02:29:51.581 --> 02:30:00.299
TRAVIS: That's a million. That's 34 to hit.

02:30:00.299 --> 02:30:01.849
LAURA: Oh, 34 to hit.

02:30:01.849 --> 02:30:04.592
MATT: Grog, you took another four points of fire
damage, reduced to two, from the fire.

02:30:04.592 --> 02:30:10.529
TRAVIS: And the damage is 24.

02:30:10.529 --> 02:30:12.076
LAURA: Oh god.

02:30:12.076 --> 02:30:13.547
TRAVIS: Last one.

02:30:13.547 --> 02:30:14.985
LAURA: Oh dear lord.

02:30:14.985 --> 02:30:19.632
SAM: So the hammer keeps coming back, and he
throws it again? Oh, wow.

02:30:19.632 --> 02:30:23.638
MATT: (throwing noises) It's nasty.

02:30:23.638 --> 02:30:26.145
TRAVIS: That is a 25.

02:30:26.145 --> 02:30:30.083
LAURA: Oh no! I think my math is wrong. Hold on.

02:30:30.083 --> 02:30:31.648
TRAVIS: You did it right.

02:30:31.648 --> 02:30:39.763
LAURA: Hold on, that doesn't make sense. 25, you
