02:31:02.676 --> 02:31:05.144
TRAVIS: And you're trapped up here with me.

02:31:05.144 --> 02:31:06.907
SAM: He'll go easy on you.

02:31:06.907 --> 02:31:14.425
LAURA: Yeah, I'm sure. Kill me quickly so I can go
pee, because I've had to for an hour now.

02:31:14.425 --> 02:31:16.281
MATT: That end your turn, Grog?

02:31:16.281 --> 02:31:17.498
TRAVIS: Yes, it does.

02:31:17.498 --> 02:31:27.429
MATT: All righty. Keyleth. You don't know where
