02:31:27.429 --> 02:31:33.551
MARISHA: I poke my head out. Do I see anything?

02:31:33.551 --> 02:31:34.999
MATT: Perception check.

02:31:34.999 --> 02:31:38.342
SAM: A bunch of smoke.

02:31:38.342 --> 02:31:42.258
MARISHA: Okay. 21.

02:31:42.258 --> 02:31:49.322
MATT: From this perspective? Not really. You do
