02:31:49.322 --> 02:31:53.965
MARISHA: Cool. I've got a good idea. I'm going to
fly up.

02:31:53.965 --> 02:31:56.266
MATT: How far up are you going to fly?

02:31:56.266 --> 02:31:59.537
MARISHA: How high is the tower? (stutters)

02:31:59.537 --> 02:32:05.711
MATT: It's about 35 feet to the top. 35 feet to
the top edge.

02:32:05.711 --> 02:32:10.857
MARISHA: I've got a flying speed of 80 feet, so
I'm going to go 40 feet up.

02:32:10.857 --> 02:32:22.656
MATT: You see Vex unconscious on the ground there,
bleeding out of the side of the mouth, and you see

02:32:22.656 --> 02:32:24.031
a giant Grog.

02:32:24.031 --> 02:32:25.581
TALIESIN: On fire.

02:32:25.581 --> 02:32:30.911
MATT: On fire, with the hammer pulling back. Grog,
you look over your shoulder and you see a big

02:32:30.911 --> 02:32:32.511
