02:32:32.511 --> 02:32:37.444
MARISHA: I look at him and I say in Draconic,
because I always forget. I go, Grog, check it out!

02:32:37.444 --> 02:32:39.472
Grog, look!

02:32:39.472 --> 02:32:47.111
MATT: The dragon goes (guttural growling speech).

02:32:47.121 --> 02:32:53.648
MARISHA: I'm going to be like, sorry, but I've
