02:34:36.919 --> 02:34:38.374
TALIESIN: 70.

02:34:38.374 --> 02:34:40.366
MARISHA: 70, total. Acid damage.

02:34:40.366 --> 02:34:48.978
MATT: (guttural growling) There's a stream of acid
that sprays down the tower over you, Grog. Go

02:34:48.978 --> 02:34:53.813
ahead and make your constitution saving throw.

02:34:53.813 --> 02:34:58.227
SAM: Tary versus a dragon. This is Dragon Slayer.

02:34:58.227 --> 02:35:02.591
TRAVIS: 21.

02:35:02.591 --> 02:35:10.035
MATT: So as the acid sprays over Grog, Grog still
stands there, covered in acid and looks at you. It

02:35:10.035 --> 02:35:11.239
puts out the fire.

02:35:11.239 --> 02:35:14.621
MARISHA: Do you have one hit point left, or some
shit?

02:35:14.621 --> 02:35:18.973
MATT: Barbarians have an ability where when they
go to zero hit points, they make a constitution

02:35:18.973 --> 02:35:21.073
