02:35:21.073 --> 02:35:23.062
LAURA: What is he at, then?

02:35:23.062 --> 02:35:23.982
TRAVIS: One.

02:35:23.982 --> 02:35:25.106
LAURA: Oh, okay.

02:35:25.106 --> 02:35:27.589
MATT: But he's still standing as the acid is
(sizzling).

02:35:27.589 --> 02:35:28.664
TRAVIS: But the fire's out!

