02:40:08.066 --> 02:40:09.844
SAM: Ooh, there's floors?

02:40:09.844 --> 02:40:10.810
MATT: Yeah.

02:40:10.810 --> 02:40:14.100
SAM: I'm going to go into the second floor, that
