MATT: All righty, top of the round. The pillars
once again (vibration) and begin to affect this

02:41:41.125 --> 02:41:47.315
area around these pillars, beginning to call
gravity to the ground. All righty. That brings us

02:41:47.315 --> 02:41:50.776
to... Vex, roll a death saving throw.

02:41:50.776 --> 02:41:54.464
LAURA: Save.

02:41:54.464 --> 02:42:00.233
MATT: Yeah, okay. Grog, your turn.

