SAM: I still have some movement, right?

02:58:07.219 --> 02:58:09.083
MATT: Yeah, you have a shit-ton of movement.

02:58:09.083 --> 02:58:11.558
SAM: I look up to see if I can see the dragon.

02:58:11.558 --> 02:58:13.625
MATT: You see the edge of a wing going (whoosh).

02:58:13.625 --> 02:58:20.862
SAM: A wing. I'm going to go to the north bunker.

02:58:20.862 --> 02:58:30.142
MATT: Over here? Okay. With that, Taryon, you head
down through here and into this north bunker over

02:58:30.142 --> 02:58:36.577
here. All right. Grog, you're technically in that
room there.

02:58:36.577 --> 02:58:40.382
SAM: All right. And now I roll my fear?

02:58:40.382 --> 02:58:42.632
MATT: Yes, now you roll your fear.

02:58:42.632 --> 02:58:48.830
SAM: 16? 15. What do I have to roll to beat this
