02:58:48.830 --> 02:58:50.504
MARISHA: Yeah, you didn't roll high enough.

02:58:50.504 --> 02:58:51.723
MATT: 18, I think it is?

02:58:51.723 --> 02:58:53.238
SAM: Jesus, I'm never going to do it.

