MATT: Only lasts a minute.

02:58:56.345 --> 02:58:57.746
SAM: Oh, okay.

02:58:57.746 --> 02:58:59.741
MATT: All right, that ends your turn, Taryon?

02:58:59.741 --> 02:59:00.973
SAM: Yep.

02:59:00.973 --> 02:59:10.974
MATT: The arcane towers (crackling) send out a
burst of energy. Roll a dexterity saving throw for

02:59:10.974 --> 02:59:13.825
your knight friend, and you roll, as well.

02:59:13.825 --> 02:59:15.133
LAURA: He's not dead?

02:59:15.133 --> 02:59:18.093
TRAVIS: No. 18?

02:59:18.093 --> 02:59:21.038
MARISHA: Oh, that's not that great. I thought that
