03:04:13.012 --> 03:04:17.010
TRAVIS: Plus five to hit. That's a 23.

03:04:17.010 --> 03:04:18.180
MARISHA: Yeah.

03:04:18.180 --> 03:04:21.699
TRAVIS: 24?

03:04:21.699 --> 03:04:25.070
MATT: All right, so 2d6 plus three to each hit.

03:04:25.070 --> 03:04:27.877
SAM: For the honor of Strongjaw!

03:04:27.877 --> 03:04:30.369
MATT: I'll protect you, my lord!

