MATT: 2d6 plus three.

03:04:34.598 --> 03:04:36.967
TRAVIS: Right, so that's 13 for the first one.

03:04:36.967 --> 03:04:38.278
MATT: 13 damage.

03:04:38.278 --> 03:04:42.203
TRAVIS: Six, seven. Ten.

03:04:42.203 --> 03:04:43.601
MARISHA: So 23 total.

03:04:43.601 --> 03:04:44.732
MATT and TRAVIS: 23 total.

03:04:44.732 --> 03:04:46.147
MARISHA: Yeah.

