TRAVIS: Plus one.

03:05:48.267 --> 03:05:49.473
MATT: So you rolled a 19?

03:05:49.473 --> 03:05:52.409
TRAVIS: It's a 20 with a plus one, but I need a
natural 20, I know.

03:05:52.409 --> 03:05:54.782
MATT: What did you roll on the dice?

03:05:54.782 --> 03:05:55.797
TRAVIS: 19.

03:05:55.797 --> 03:05:56.870
LAURA: Plus one.

03:05:56.870 --> 03:05:58.005
MATT: That's a 20.

03:05:58.005 --> 03:05:59.157
MARISHA: The 20 is what I had.

03:05:59.157 --> 03:06:00.172
MATT: Yeah, so he saves.

03:06:00.172 --> 03:06:02.511
MARISHA: You are lying to me. You are fucking
lying!

03:06:02.511 --> 03:06:03.883
MATT: It's what he rolled!

03:06:03.883 --> 03:06:06.985
TALIESIN: This is what's been happening all
night.

03:06:06.985 --> 03:06:14.115
SAM: The plane of existence. You break it!

03:06:14.115 --> 03:06:19.961
MATT: You resist the effect as Keyleth is holding
onto you, and she slowly lets go,

03:06:19.961 --> 03:06:21.308
