TALIESIN: You have your bonus and your movement.

03:06:23.603 --> 03:06:24.946
MARISHA: I have a bonus and a movement.

03:06:24.946 --> 03:06:25.866
MATT: Yes, you do.

03:06:25.866 --> 03:06:28.310
MARISHA: Okay. Oh god.

03:06:28.310 --> 03:06:29.718
LAURA: Run away!

03:06:29.718 --> 03:06:32.973
MATT: That's your 7th-level spell, gone.

03:06:32.973 --> 03:06:35.720
