MATT: Grasping Vine is 4th-level. You can't cast
it.

03:07:02.566 --> 03:07:15.625
MARISHA: Fuck! Okay. I will do... options are
dwindling very quickly.

03:07:15.625 --> 03:07:18.220
LAURA: Tary will be the survivor because he's
hiding.

