MARISHA: Okay. I'm going to do a bonus action to
heal myself. Healing Word. Let's do a 3rd-level

03:07:42.138 --> 03:07:44.047
Healing Word.

03:07:44.047 --> 03:07:48.024
MATT: 2nd-level Healing Word. You can't do more
than 2nd-level.

03:07:48.024 --> 03:07:57.143
MARISHA: Sorry. You're right. 2nd-level Healing
Word. So it's 2d4. Oh my god.

03:07:57.143 --> 03:08:01.904
TALIESIN: You are the luckiest motherfucker. This
has all been just--

03:08:01.904 --> 03:08:04.976
LAURA: Why couldn't he have rolled like he did on
the one-shot, where

03:08:04.976 --> 03:08:07.068
