03:09:25.462 --> 03:09:26.659
MARISHA: Yeah.

03:09:26.659 --> 03:09:28.117
MATT: 2d6 plus three.

03:09:28.117 --> 03:09:36.626
TRAVIS: Six.

03:09:36.626 --> 03:09:38.762
MATT: Six points of damage to you.

03:09:38.762 --> 03:09:50.001
MARISHA: Just six? Six from the knight. Okay, that
puts me at 46.

03:09:50.001 --> 03:09:52.116
TRAVIS: 28 to hit from me.

03:09:52.116 --> 03:09:54.076
SAM: That hits.

03:09:54.076 --> 03:10:00.298
TRAVIS: 21 points of damage.

03:10:00.298 --> 03:10:01.826
SAM: She's okay.

03:10:01.826 --> 03:10:05.674
MATT: Keyleth, you turn, you run. Make an
athletics check, please.

03:10:05.674 --> 03:10:09.212
MARISHA: Do I have advantage on this?

03:10:09.212 --> 03:10:10.639
MATT: No.

03:10:10.639 --> 03:10:15.825
MARISHA: I'm so bad at my athletics. I'm always
so bad! 12.

03:10:15.825 --> 03:10:19.615
MATT: It's okay. You didn't have to roll high.
