03:10:32.676 --> 03:10:34.825
MARISHA: Ugh, I fucking twisted my ankle.

03:10:34.825 --> 03:10:37.074
MATT: Yeah, it hurt. It pops a little bit, but
you're there.

03:10:37.074 --> 03:10:40.429
MARISHA: How much? Four points?

03:10:40.429 --> 03:10:54.167
MATT: Four points, yeah. All right. That's your
turn, Keyleth? Taryon. You're way over here.

03:10:54.167 --> 03:11:04.481
SAM: Fly out, fly up. Halfway up.

03:11:04.481 --> 03:11:06.986
MATT: Halfway up? About there.

