SAM: We're dealing with three dimensions, here.

03:11:18.924 --> 03:11:22.378
MATT: You could hit both of them. All three of
them with it.

03:11:22.378 --> 03:11:24.477
SAM: I will aim that way.

03:11:24.477 --> 03:11:29.172
MATT: You have to pull back a lot, like over
here.

03:11:29.172 --> 03:11:31.266
MARISHA: What the fuck kind of cone are you
