MATT: Yeah, they're all within 60 feet.

03:11:48.549 --> 03:11:50.092
TALIESIN: Oh my god.

03:11:50.092 --> 03:11:52.264
MARISHA: Tary wins.

03:11:52.264 --> 03:11:55.731
SAM: d8 again?

