03:12:20.711 --> 03:12:21.974
MARISHA: Dexterity saves?

03:12:21.974 --> 03:12:24.179
MATT: Dexterity saving throw, yeah.

03:12:24.179 --> 03:12:25.999
MARISHA: Oh, that's good!

